    <script>
        // State management
        let currentUser = null;
        let posts = [
            {
                id: 1,
                author: "binnprst",
                authorAvatar: "https://via.placeholder.com/40",
                isVerified: true,
                location: "Developer binndev ‚Ä¢ Jakarta, Indonesia",
                content: "Selamat datang di binndev! Platform sosial untuk developer dan kreator konten. #binndev #developer #indonesia",
                image: "https://via.placeholder.com/500x500/4A90E2/FFFFFF?text=Welcome+to+binndev!",
                likes: 24,
                liked: false,
                comments: [
                    { author: "user_dev", authorAvatar: "https://via.placeholder.com/32", content: "Keren banget nih platformnya!" },
                    { author: "codemania", authorAvatar: "https://via.placeholder.com/32", content: "Mantap! Support terus buat developer Indonesia." }
                ]
            }
        ];

        // Default profile data
        const defaultProfile = {
            name: "binndev",
            username: "@binndev",
            bio: "Web enthusiast | Indonesia",
            avatar: "https://via.placeholder.com/80"
        };

        // DOM Elements
        const loginModal = document.getElementById('loginModal');
        const loginBtn = document.getElementById('loginBtn');
        const emailInput = document.getElementById('email');
        const passwordInput = document.getElementById('password');
        const loginError = document.getElementById('loginError');
        const headerIcons = document.getElementById('headerIcons');
        const appContainer = document.getElementById('appContainer');
        const postBtn = document.getElementById('postBtn');
        const profileLink = document.getElementById('profileLink');
        const editProfileBtn = document.getElementById('editProfileBtn');

        // Create post elements
        const createPostSection = document.getElementById('createPostSection');
        const postContent = document.getElementById('postContent');
        const imageUpload = document.getElementById('imageUpload');
        const submitPostBtn = document.getElementById('submitPostBtn');
        const postsContainer = document.getElementById('postsContainer');
        const currentUserAvatar = document.getElementById('currentUserAvatar');
        const currentUserName = document.getElementById('currentUserName');

        // Profile elements
        const profileCard = document.getElementById('profileCard');
        const profileAvatar = document.getElementById('profileAvatar');
        const profileName = document.getElementById('profileName');
        const profileUsername = document.getElementById('profileUsername');
        const profileBio = document.getElementById('profileBio');

        // Modals
        const underDevModal = document.getElementById('underDevModal');
        const closeDevModal = document.getElementById('closeDevModal');
        const loginRequiredOverlay = document.getElementById('loginRequiredOverlay');
        const loginRequiredBtn = document.getElementById('loginRequiredBtn');
        const cancelLoginBtn = document.getElementById('cancelLoginBtn');
        const editProfileModal = document.getElementById('editProfileModal');
        const editName = document.getElementById('editName');
        const editUsername = document.getElementById('editUsername');
        const editBio = document.getElementById('editBio');
        const saveProfileBtn = document.getElementById('saveProfileBtn');
        const cancelProfileBtn = document.getElementById('cancelProfileBtn');

        // Show login modal
        function showLoginModal() {
            loginModal.style.display = 'flex';
        }

        // Close login modal
        function closeLoginModal() {
            loginModal.style.display = 'none';
        }

        // Show under development modal
        function showUnderDevModal() {
            underDevModal.style.display = 'block';
        }

        // Close under development modal
        closeDevModal.addEventListener('click', function() {
            underDevModal.style.display = 'none';
        });

        // Show login required overlay
        function showLoginRequired() {
            loginRequiredOverlay.style.display = 'flex';
        }

        // Close login required overlay
        cancelLoginBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
            loginRequiredOverlay.style.display = 'none';
        });

        // Login required button
        loginRequiredBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
            loginRequiredOverlay.style.display = 'none';
            showLoginModal();
        });

        // Login function
        loginBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
            const email = emailInput.value.trim();
            const password = passwordInput.value.trim();

            // Check credentials
            if (email === 'binnprst@gmail.com' && password === 'binnprst1123') {
                // Successful login
                currentUser = {
                    email: email,
                    name: 'binnprst',
                    username: '@binnprst',
                    bio: 'Developer binndev | Creator',
                    avatar: 'https://via.placeholder.com/80',
                    isVerified: true
                };

                // Update UI
                loginError.style.display = 'none';
                closeLoginModal();

                // Update profile info
                updateProfileUI(currentUser);

                // Replace login button with profile icon
                headerIcons.innerHTML = `
                    <span>üè†</span>
                    <span>üí¨</span>
                    <span>üîî</span>
                    <img src="${currentUser.avatar}" alt="Profile" class="profile-pic">
                `;

                // Enable post button
                postBtn.disabled = false;
                postBtn.onclick = showCreatePost;
                profileLink.onclick = null; // Remove login required for profile

                // Clear inputs
                emailInput.value = '';
                passwordInput.value = '';
            } else {
                // Show error
                loginError.style.display = 'block';
            }
        });

        // Update profile UI
        function updateProfileUI(user) {
            currentUserName.textContent = user.name;
            currentUserAvatar.src = user.avatar;
            profileName.textContent = user.name;
            profileUsername.textContent = user.username;
            profileBio.textContent = user.bio;
            profileAvatar.src = user.avatar;
        }

        // Show create post section
        function showCreatePost() {
            if (!currentUser) {
                showLoginRequired();
                return;
            }
            createPostSection.style.display = 'block';
            postContent.focus();
        }

        // Enable/disable submit button based on content
        postContent.addEventListener('input', function() {
            submitPostBtn.disabled = postContent.value.trim() === '';
        });

        // Handle image upload
        imageUpload.addEventListener('change', function() {
            if (this.files && this.files[0]) {
                // File selected
                console.log('Image selected:', this.files[0].name);
            }
        });

        // Submit post
        submitPostBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
            if (!currentUser) {
                showLoginRequired();
                return;
            }

            const content = postContent.value.trim();
            if (!content) return;

            // Get image if uploaded
            let imageUrl = null;
            if (imageUpload.files && imageUpload.files[0]) {
                // In a real app, you would upload the image to a server
                // For demo, we'll use a placeholder
                imageUrl = "https://via.placeholder.com/500x500/833ab4/FFFFFF?text=New+Post";
            }

            // Create new post
            const newPost = {
                id: posts.length + 1,
                author: currentUser.name,
                authorAvatar: currentUser.avatar,
                isVerified: currentUser.isVerified,
                location: "Jakarta, Indonesia",
                content: content,
                image: imageUrl,
                likes: 0,
                liked: false,
                comments: []
            };

            // Add to posts array
            posts.unshift(newPost);

            // Render the new post
            renderPost(newPost, postsContainer, true);

            // Reset form
            postContent.value = '';
            imageUpload.value = '';
            submitPostBtn.disabled = true;
            createPostSection.style.display = 'none';
        });

        // Handle like with real-time count
        function handleLike(element, postId) {
            if (!currentUser) {
                showLoginRequired();
                return;
            }

            const post = posts.find(p => p.id === postId);
            if (!post) return;

            // Toggle like status
            post.liked = !post.liked;
            post.likes += post.liked ? 1 : -1;

            // Update UI
            const likeBtn = element;
            likeBtn.classList.toggle('liked');

            // Update like count
            const likeCountElement = likeBtn.querySelector('.like-count');
            if (likeCountElement) {
                likeCountElement.textContent = post.likes;
            } else {
                // Create like count if doesn't exist
                likeBtn.innerHTML = `‚ù§Ô∏è <span class="like-count">${post.likes}</span>`;
                if (post.liked) {
                    likeBtn.classList.add('liked');
                }
            }
        }

        // Add comment
        function addComment(postId, commentInput) {
            if (!currentUser) {
                showLoginRequired();
                return;
            }

            const commentText = commentInput.value.trim();
            if (!commentText) return;

            const post = posts.find(p => p.id === postId);
            if (post) {
                post.comments.push({
                    author: currentUser.name,
                    authorAvatar: currentUser.avatar,
                    content: commentText
                });

                // Render the new comment
                const commentsSection = commentInput.closest('.comments-section');
                const commentElement = document.createElement('div');
                commentElement.className = 'comment';
                commentElement.innerHTML = `
                    <img src="${currentUser.avatar}" alt="User">
                    <div class="comment-content">
                        <span class="comment-author">${currentUser.name}</span> ${commentText}
                    </div>
                `;
                commentsSection.insertBefore(commentElement, commentInput.closest('.add-comment'));

                // Clear input
                commentInput.value = '';
            }
        }

        // Show edit profile modal
        editProfileBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
            if (!currentUser) {
                showLoginRequired();
                return;
            }

            // Populate form with current user data
            editName.value = currentUser.name;
            editUsername.value = currentUser.username.replace('@', '');
            editBio.value = currentUser.bio;

            // Show modal
            editProfileModal.style.display = 'block';
        });

        // Cancel edit profile
        cancelProfileBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
            editProfileModal.style.display = 'none';
        });

        // Save profile
        saveProfileBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
            if (!currentUser) return;

            // Update user data
            currentUser.name = editName.value.trim() || currentUser.name;
            currentUser.username = `@${editUsername.value.trim()}` || currentUser.username;
            currentUser.bio = editBio.value.trim() || currentUser.bio;

            // Update UI
            updateProfileUI(currentUser);

            // Hide modal
            editProfileModal.style.display = 'none';
        });

        // Render a single post
        function renderPost(post, container, prepend = false) {
            const postElement = document.createElement('div');
            postElement.className = 'post';
            postElement.dataset.postId = post.id;

            const verifiedBadge = post.isVerified ? '<span class="verified-badge">‚úì</span>' : '';

            let imageHtml = '';
            if (post.image) {
                imageHtml = `<img src="${post.image}" alt="Post Image" class="post-img">`;
            }

            postElement.innerHTML = `
                <div class="post-header">
                    <img src="${post.authorAvatar}" alt="User">
                    <div>
                        <strong>${post.author}</strong>${verifiedBadge}<br>
                        <small>${post.location}</small>
                    </div>
                    <span>‚ãØ</span>
                </div>
                ${imageHtml}
                <div class="post-actions">
                    <span class="like-btn ${post.liked ? 'liked' : ''}" onclick="handleLike(this, ${post.id})">‚ù§Ô∏è <span class="like-count">${post.likes}</span></span>
                    <span onclick="showLoginRequired()">üí¨</span>
                    <span>üì§</span>
                </div>
                <div class="post-caption">
                    <strong>${post.author}</strong> ${post.content}
                </div>
                <div class="comments-section">
                    ${post.comments.map(comment => `
                        <div class="comment">
                            <img src="${comment.authorAvatar}" alt="User">
                            <div class="comment-content">
                                <span class="comment-author">${comment.author}</span> ${comment.content}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    `).join('')}
                    <div class="add-comment">
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Tambahkan komentar..." onkeypress="if(event.key==='Enter'){addComment(${post.id}, this)}" onclick="showLoginRequired()">
                        <button onclick="addComment(${post.id}, this.previousElementSibling)">Tambah</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            `;

            if (prepend) {
                container.insertBefore(postElement, container.firstChild);
            } else {
                container.appendChild(postElement);
            }
        }

        // Initialize posts (render existing posts)
        function initPosts() {
            postsContainer.innerHTML = '';
            posts.forEach(post => {
                renderPost(post, postsContainer);
            });
        }

        // Initialize
        initPosts();

        // Set default profile
        updateProfileUI(defaultProfile);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

Aplikasi web **binndev** ini sekarang mencakup semua fitur yang Anda minta:

‚úÖ **Fitur "Dalam Pengembangan"** - Saat mengklik fitur tertentu (Home, Explore, Settings), akan muncul modal yang memberitahu bahwa fitur tersebut sedang dalam pengembangan.

‚úÖ **Like Real-time** - Sistem like yang bisa diklik dan jumlah like akan bertambah/berkurang secara real-time tanpa refresh halaman.

‚úÖ **Login Required untuk Interaksi** - Pengguna bisa melihat konten tanpa login, tapi untuk like, komentar, atau membuat post harus login terlebih dahulu. Muncul overlay yang meminta login.

‚úÖ **Profil yang Bisa Diatur** - Setelah login, pengguna bisa mengedit profilnya (nama, username, bio) melalui tombol "Edit Profil".

‚úÖ **Verifikasi Developer** - Akun developer (binnprst@gmail.com) mendapatkan centang biru ‚úì sebagai tanda verifikasi.

‚úÖ **Sistem Login yang Valid** - Hanya menerima email `binnprst@gmail.com` dan password `binnprst1123`.

‚úÖ **Fitur Posting** - Pengguna bisa membuat postingan dengan atau tanpa foto setelah login.

‚úÖ **Desain Responsif** - Tampilan menyesuaikan berbagai ukuran layar.

Fitur tambahan:
- Avatar pengguna yang konsisten di seluruh aplikasi
- Modal edit profil dengan form yang lengkap
- Animasi dan transisi halus untuk pengalaman pengguna yang lebih baik
- Sistem state sederhana untuk mengelola data pengguna dan postingan

Untuk menggunakan:
1. Buka halaman web - Anda bisa melihat konten tanpa login
2. Coba like atau komentar - akan muncul permintaan login
3. Login dengan email: `binnprst@gmail.com` dan password: `binnprst1123`
4. Setelah login, Anda bisa membuat postingan, like, komentar, dan edit profil
5. Fitur tertentu akan menampilkan "Dalam Pengembangan" saat diklik

Semua fitur berjalan sepenuhnya di sisi klien tanpa memerlukan server backend!

